### Account URL

Once created, this account will be accessible at:

`https://{{ snowflake_org_name | lower }}-{{ new_account_name | lower }}.snowflakecomputing.com`

### Technical Configuration

| Parameter | Value |
|-----------|-------|
| **Edition** | {{ new_account_edition }} |
| **Cloud Region** | {{ new_account_region }} |

{%- if new_account_edition == "Standard" %}

**Standard Edition** provides core Snowflake features suitable for development and cost-sensitive workloads.

{%- elif new_account_edition == "Enterprise" %}

**Enterprise Edition** provides advanced features including:
- Multi-cluster warehouses
- Up to 90-day Time Travel
- Column-level security
- Failover/Failback support

{%- elif new_account_edition == "Business Critical" %}

**Business Critical Edition** provides the highest level of security and compliance:
- HIPAA and PCI DSS compliance
- Customer-managed encryption keys
- Private connectivity options

{%- endif %}

### Initial Administrator

| Parameter | Value |
|-----------|-------|
| **Username** | {{ new_account_admin_name }} |
